---
---

<section class="testimonials">
  <div class="testimonial-stage">
    <div class="section-label">Words from Clients</div>
    <div id="quotes" aria-live="polite">
      <article class="quote">
        <p class="quote-text">Josiah was an absolute pleasure to work with. He showed up on time, kept things easy and low-pressure, and gave great direction throughout the whole shoot — which made a huge difference since I'm not exactly used to being in front of a camera. We shot outdoors and the results were better than I expected. If you need professional headshots done right, Josiah's your guy.</p>
        <div class="quote-meta">
          <span class="who">Katheryn Hammonds</span>
          <span class="what">Director of Marketing · Hammonds Media &amp; Marketing</span>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    background: var(--ink-2);
    padding: 180px 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .testimonials::before,
  .testimonials::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 80px;
    right: 80px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--rule);
  }

  .testimonials::before { top: 0; }
  .testimonials::after { bottom: 0; }

  .testimonial-stage {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.42em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .section-label::before {
    content: "";
    width: 28px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 2.2vw, 34px);
    line-height: 1.38;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin: 0 auto 44px;
    max-width: 36ch;
    text-wrap: balance;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  .quote-text::before {
    content: "\201C";
    color: var(--accent);
    font-style: normal;
    margin-right: 6px;
  }

  .quote-text::after {
    content: "\201D";
    color: var(--accent);
    font-style: normal;
    margin-left: 6px;
  }

  .quote-meta {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.34em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .quote-meta .who {
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .quote-meta .what {
    color: var(--taupe);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .testimonials { padding: 130px 28px; }
    .testimonials::before,
    .testimonials::after { left: 28px; right: 28px; }
  }
</style>
